《'''塞勒姆：傳說、附魔和怪物的秘密檔案'''》（{{lang-en|''S.A.L.E.M.: The Secret Archive of Legends, Enchantments, and Monsters''}}）是一部美國[[奇幻作品|奇幻]][[神秘小說|懸疑]]{{le|網路電視劇|Web television|網路電視動畫}}，由[[酷兒|酷兒]]薩曼莎·「薩姆」·索耶（{{lang|en|Samantha "Sam" Sawyer}}）所創作，改編自索耶的未出版漫畫《塞勒姆》（{{lang|en|''S.A.L.E.M.''}}），講述[[非二元性別|非二元性別]]的[[神秘生物列表|神秘生物]]塞勒姆（{{lang|en|Salem}}）與同伴們的冒險旅程<ref name="Patch(2020-02-04)" /><ref name="Starshine(2019-12-18)" />。動畫由[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]上的眾籌活動資助<ref name="TheGeekLyfe(2020-10-06)">{{cite web|url=https://thegeeklyfe.com/interview-with-creator-sincerely-sam-on-the-salem-kickstarter/|title=INTERVIEW WITH CREATOR SINCERELY SAM ON THE SALEM KICKSTARTER!|last=Murillo|first=DeAngelo|work=The Geek Lyfe|date=2020-10-06|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092458/https://thegeeklyfe.com/interview-with-creator-sincerely-sam-on-the-salem-kickstarter/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="V13(2020-01-10)">{{cite web|url=https://v13.net/2020/01/comic-book-artist-sam-sawyer-discusses-her-graphic-novel-salem-and-development-of-its-animated-series-w-audio/|title=Comic Book Artist SAM SAWYER Discusses Her Graphic Novel Salem and Development of its Animated Series [w/ Audio]|last=Young|first=Alex|work=V13|date=2020-01-10|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092429/https://v13.net/2020/01/comic-book-artist-sam-sawyer-discusses-her-graphic-novel-salem-and-development-of-its-animated-series-w-audio/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

索耶表示，該劇受到《[[愛酷一族|愛酷一族]]》、《[[膽小狗英雄|膽小狗英雄]]》和《{{le|外星入侵者齊姆|Invader Zim}}》的影響。該劇播映日目前未定。

== 劇情 ==
故事背景設定於美國[[西維吉尼亞州|西維吉尼亞州]]的虛構城市空心視界（{{lang|en|Hollow Watch}}）中，講述[[非二元性別|非二元性別]]的[[神秘生物列表|神秘生物]]塞勒姆，沒有核心身份或性別，為了探索自己真實身份而展開冒險。一本附魔的書、攝影師奧利佛和靈媒佩特拉加入了塞勒姆的這趟旅途，眾人共同穿梭於「妖精、地精和其他神秘世界」。<ref name="MackenzieAmyx(2020-02-15)">{{cite web|url=https://mackenzieamyx.com/index.php/2020/02/15/interview-with-sam-sawyer/|title=Interview with Sam Sawyer|work=Mackenzie Amyx|date=2020-02-15|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092456/https://mackenzieamyx.com/index.php/2020/02/15/interview-with-sam-sawyer/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AlbuquerqueJournal(2020-01-17)" />

