== 製作 ==
動畫改編自主創[[酷兒|酷兒]]薩曼莎·「薩姆」·索耶（{{lang|en|Samantha "Sam" Sawyer}}）的未出版漫畫《塞勒姆》（{{lang|en|''S.A.L.E.M.''}}）<ref name="Patch(2020-02-04)">{{cite web|url=https://patch.com/nevada/lasvegas/artist-sam-sawyer-lvl-expo|title=Artist Sam Sawyer to LVL UP Expo|last=Johnson|first=Bill|work={{le|Patch (網站)|Patch (website)|Patch}}|date=2020-02-04|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092242/https://patch.com/nevada/lasvegas/artist-sam-sawyer-lvl-expo|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Starshine(2019-12-18)">{{cite web|url=https://starshinemag.net/artist-sam-sawyer-creates-first-animated-series-with-non-binary-hero/|title=Artist Sam Sawyer Creates First Animated Series with Non-Binary Hero|last=Lo|first=Sandy|work=Starshine Magazine|date=2019-12-18|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092451/https://starshinemag.net/artist-sam-sawyer-creates-first-animated-series-with-non-binary-hero/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於2013年起構思改編動畫，直到2018年11月才開始由{{le|傑夫·「史旺比」·馬許|Jeff "Swampy" Marsh|史旺比·馬許}}的衝浪者傑克製作（{{lang|en|Surfer Jack Productions}}）公司進行主要製作<ref name="PipersPicks.TV(2019-11-15)">{{cite web|url=https://piperspicks.tv/2019/11/15/salem-animated-series-creator-sam-sawyer-cryptids-nonbinary-witchcraft/|title=SALEM Animated Series Creator Sam Sawyer, Cryptids, Nonbinary & Witchcraft|author=TeamPiper|work=PipersPicks.TV|date=2019-11-15|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092515/https://piperspicks.tv/2019/11/15/salem-animated-series-creator-sam-sawyer-cryptids-nonbinary-witchcraft/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。動畫在[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]上發起眾籌活動，以募集資金<ref name="TheGeekLyfe(2020-10-06)" /><ref name="V13(2020-01-10)" /><ref name="AnimationForAdults(2019-10-27)">{{cite web|url=https://www.animationforadults.com/2019/10/kickstart-this-salem-secret-archive-of.html|title=KICKSTART THIS! "S.A.L.E.M: THE SECRET ARCHIVE OF LEGENDS, ENCHANTMENTS AND MONSTERS"|last=Ward|first=Rachael|work=Animation For Adults|date=2019-10-27|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092243/https://www.animationforadults.com/2019/10/kickstart-this-salem-secret-archive-of.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。馬許將擔任執行製片人兼配音導演，Q·福爾蒂（{{lang|en|Q Fortier}}）則擔任一級監製。此外，{{lang|en|LostSock LLC}}的蘭迪·亞伯拉罕（{{lang|en|Randy Abrams}}）將擔任執行製片人。<ref name="SalemYoutube(2020-12-11)">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQ3OxC9XlLo|title=SALEM Cast and Crew Discuss The Animation Process|work=Salem Series|format=Youtube|date=2020-12-11|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092523/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQ3OxC9XlLo|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[蘿拉·貝莉|蘿拉·貝莉]]、{{le|亞當·麥卡爾斯|Adam McArthur}}、{{le|瑞兒·唐斯|Riele Downs}}及{{le|羅伯·保羅森|Rob Paulsen}}擔任幾名主角的配音員，分別為塞勒姆（{{lang|en|Salem}}）、奧利佛（{{lang|en|Oliver}}）、佩特拉（{{lang|en|Petra}}），以及隱密後裔（{{lang|en|The Cryptorium}}）和布格曼（{{lang|en|Boogeyman}}）<ref name="AnimationForAdults(2019-10-27)" />。2020年2月，長度一季的集數已製作完成，每集達11至12分鐘長<ref name="AuthorityMagazine(2020-02-14)">{{cite web|url=https://medium.com/authority-magazine/rising-star-sam-sawyer-our-words-are-powerful-and-i-think-people-need-to-start-understanding-bac33c818996|title=Rising Star Sam Sawyer: “Our words are powerful, and I think people need to start understanding that more; One simple smile or kind word can change someone’s life”|work=Authority Magazine|date=2020-02-14|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092451/https://medium.com/authority-magazine/rising-star-sam-sawyer-our-words-are-powerful-and-i-think-people-need-to-start-understanding-bac33c818996|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TheHollywoodTimes(2020-02-21)">{{cite web|url=https://thehollywoodtimes.today/animation-gets-a-new-look-as-artist-sam-sawyer-creates-the-first-series-featuring-a-non-binary-hero/|title=Animation Gets a New Look as Artist Sam Sawyer Creates the First Series Featuring a Non-Binary Hero|last=Shields|first=Judy|work=The Hollywood Times|date=2020-02-21|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092255/https://thehollywoodtimes.today/animation-gets-a-new-look-as-artist-sam-sawyer-creates-the-first-series-featuring-a-non-binary-hero/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

索耶在2020年1月的一次採訪中表示，她一直都知道這個故事是關於「與眾不同的人」，並指出主角群歸類於[[非二元性別|非二元性別]]，並補充說，創作方以講述殘疾人、膚色，以及「不認同性別的人」來展開故事<ref name="AlbuquerqueJournal(2020-01-17)">{{cite web|url=https://www.abqjournal.com/1410437/monster-maker.html|title=Monster maker|last=Gomez|first=Adrian|work={{le|阿爾伯克基日報|Albuquerque Journal|Albuquerque Journal}}|date=2020-01-17|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092248/https://www.abqjournal.com/1410437/monster-maker.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，索耶表示，該劇受到《[[愛酷一族|愛酷一族]]》、《[[膽小狗英雄|膽小狗英雄]]》和《{{le|外星入侵者齊姆|Invader Zim}}》的影響<ref name="AnimationForAdults(2019-10-27)" /><ref name="AlbuquerqueComicCon">{{cite web|url=https://albuquerquecomiccon.com/sam-sawyer/|title=Sam Sawyer|work=Albuquerque Comic Con|date=October 2019|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216092444/https://albuquerquecomiccon.com/sam-sawyer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

